        "en": "<p>A soil remediation expert is an independent expert recognised by the senior civil servant of the Public Waste Agency of Flanders (Openbare Vlaamse Afvalstoffenmaatschappij/OVAM). There are two types of soil remediation experts:</p><ul><li><strong>Type 1</strong> recognised soil remediation experts are recognised to carry out <strong>exploratory soil investigations</strong> and prepare <strong>reports</strong> in the context of <strong>earthworks</strong>.</li><li><strong>Type 2</strong> recognised soil remediation experts may perform <strong>all the tasks</strong> assigned to soil remediation experts under the Soil Decree (and its implementing orders).</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://ovam.vlaanderen.be/lijstbsd\">Consult the list of soil remediation experts</a> on the Public Waste Agency of Flanders (OVAM) website.</p>",
